reviewText: HORRENDOUS SUBTITLES ever! Nothing made sense in any episode. Got a HEADACHE just previewing dvds!  What a waste of my time in ordering, previewing and returning! The one star is for seller's prompt return although it's a pain for me!
I love all the Korean dramas I've seen with Choi Kang Hee. Very quirky and charming. She seems to take a few more chances with her characters than a lot of the other actresses in this genre.
